Расчет предварительного поиска

This is the official set of GitHub Training courseware including outlines, topic-specific guides, examples, and slides provided under the CC BY 3.0 license to aid schools, universities, user groups, hackathons, corporate lunch-and-learns and other educational outlets in teaching Git and GitHub. In short, you should take these materials and make the development world a better place by leveraging them to teach a class or give a conference talk. Do a quick check that you are using the materials in the spirit of the license and then go forth and spread the good Git and GitHub news.
